Berjalan lurus.

00:08:35.848 --> 00:08:36.928
Oh!

00:08:37.448 --> 00:08:38.408
Dan..

00:08:39.688 --> 00:08:40.568
Ini dia!

00:08:57.408 --> 00:08:58.328
Wow!

