... dicampur dengan
kristal transparan.

00:11:30.928 --> 00:11:31.808
Apa?

00:11:32.408 --> 00:11:33.688
Teh, Bu.

00:11:37.448 --> 00:11:40.368
Kami minum teh dengan
beberapa makanan ringan.

00:11:40.728 --> 00:11:43.888
